{"tid":2315993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[F35 mola]新加坡副總理王瑞傑冀新加坡與中國加強後疫情時代合作","createTime":"2020-12-07T14:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T14:10:58.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e43f6562710aeb8f7b2c8666b10979496eb96345","tid":2315993,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564051-20201207.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564051-20201207.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=c0ba1c3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564051-20201207.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c48903bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564051-20201207.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n新加坡副總理王瑞傑表示，希望與中國加強後疫情時代合作，共同拓展互聯互通、數字化和可持續發展三大領域合作，為區域經濟發展做出貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n他在中新雙邊合作聯合委員會召前前夕接受新華社專訪。<br />\n<br />\n王瑞傑強調，兩國在蘇州、天津和重慶的三個政府間合作項目，是雙邊關係欣欣向榮的最佳體現。兩國合作的領域，從工業擴大至可持續城市發展、互聯互通，以及數字經濟等新領域。<br />\n<br />\n王瑞傑又說，新加坡支持「一帶一路」倡議，並為沿線國家提供投資和金融服務渠道，協助這些國家展開可持續的基礎設施建設。"},{"pid":"577575c258ee4a6ce1fed4de01fcb6738169ff88","tid":2315993,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:06:59.000Z","msg":"奶到雪雪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nXJPSAR"},{"pid":"de73180e177a812f3e93331dd90890bfac55b46a","tid":2315993,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:10:58.000Z","msg":"李顯龍接班人，繼續奶共，睇嚟猩加坡選擇站邊中共了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBO1tEw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBO1tEw.png&h=05dd49c6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}